### Método para crear un curso con archivos subidos
POST http://localhost:4300/api/v1/courses/create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=--BoundaryCustom

----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title_course"

Curso de Prueba 2
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description_course"

Este es un curso de prueba para demostrar la subida de archivos.
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price_course"

49.99
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="duration_course"

10
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="thumbnail_course"; filename="thumbnail.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

./uploads/sample_thumbnail.jpg
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="preview_video"; filename="preview.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

./uploads/sample_preview.mp4
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="short_description"

Este curso cubre los conceptos básicos de la programación.
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="level_course"

intermediate
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type_course"

premium
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="instructor_id"

2
----BoundaryCustom
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="slug_course"

curso-de-prueba-2
----BoundaryCustom----

